        ---------------------

        This virus damages some files, which are needed from the the PhobOS
        mailbox system. I heard that PhobOS is a  "scene" mailbox programm,
        which is very wide spread in the south of Germany.
        The PStats programm was written in GFABASIC.  As a result I  think, 
        the author of the virus has the sourcecode of the PStats  programm.
        Is it maybe spreaded together  with the PhobOS system?  This time I
        need your help. I have heard that this system is wide spread in the
        south of GERMANY.

	         Detection and Repairroutine tested on 19.01.1993.


