 --------------------

 - Fixed some problems with INTUITION 
   (I have not known that a CLOSEWINDOW in Window TAGS caused the system
     to paint a smaller bar than the normal menu bar). It took hours to
     fix the problem!
 - added workbenchstartcode                                                  
 - optimized some routines in the HD Support menu.
 - a new decrunch Library was added.                                
 - fixed some problems with Kickstart 1.3. The detection routines were broken
   down...
 - Major Bug removed: Trackdisk device destination adresses must be in 
   CHIPRAM, if you use Kickstart 1.2. or Kickstart 1.3.
   Due to coding only on Kickstart 2.04 and Kickstart 3.00 I "forgot" this
   bug. Thanx to Stefan Noelle for testing it.
 - Added Support for the A1200 version of the 39.106 Kickstart release
   from Commodore.

